                    "body": "I think that we can close this.\r\nWe need {{AppendValues(const value_type* values, int64_t length, const int32_t* valid_bytes = NULLPTR)}} for my use case. But it's not suitable to handle in this issue. Because existing {{AppendValues()}} variants already accept bytemap. They just don't accept 4bytemap.",
